thread.title: Adrianne Nessel
thread.title_full: Ink Station reviewed by Adrianne Nessel

author: Adrianne Nessel
title: Adrianne Nessel
text: As a university student I use a fair amount of ink. I also have a limited budget to buy this ink. Buying from Ink Station, I regularly save up to $10.00 per cartridge and it gets delivered free of charge in a couple of days. Great prices, excellent & efficient service.
